		{
			description: [
				"One &4&lbite&r&r, and you’re on the &6&lclock&r&r. There is a &2&lchance&r zombies can infect you if they hit you."
				""
				"&4&lFour&r&r stages of infection, with &l&7death&r&r waiting at the end. Fight hard, or join the ranks of the undead."
				""
				"Zombie hordes will attack your location in waves every &4&l10&r&r days. Be prepared."
				""
				"Your mission: carve out a safe haven, fortify your defenses, and endure the relentless chaos of the zombie apocalypse."
