		{
			description: ["Grass and foliage colors will change throughout the year, and in the &b&lwinter&r&r, temperatures will shift and allow for &lsnow&r to fall in some biomes that don't normally receive any. Seasons also affect various other features, like crop &2&lgrowth&r, &9&lweather&r, and more!"]
