		{
			description: [
				"Though the cure has been discovered, it came far too late to save the &4&lfallen&r&r. "
				""
				"The vaccine is crafted from &l&aFoxweed flowers&r&r found in most forests. In addition to curing the infection, vaccines also give you over &b&l5 minutes of immunity&r&r to the infection."
				""
				"Alternatively, &l&egolden apples&r&r can also cure an infection, though they do not provide any further immunity."
				""
				"The world lies in ruins, overrun by the undead, and survival now rests on &4&lyour&r&r shoulders."
