		{
			description: [
				"JEI/EMI is a very helpful tool. It is the thing on the right of your inventory. In there you can do various things:"
				""
				"- Search for a item in the &asearchbar&r at the bottom of your inventory (&efilter by mod with @ infront&r)"
				"- Click on it and you will see its &acrafting recipe&r"
				"- click on a item in the crafting recipe to find out &ahow to craft it&r"
				"- for many items, you can &anavigate on the top bar&r to see all the usecases of the item"
				""
				"See next page for hotkeys "
				"(all default keybinds) ->"
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"Hotkeys:"
				"- hover over an item and press &aR&r (default) to view its recipe"
				"- hover over an item and press &aU&r (default) to view its uses"
				"- &adouble-click&r on the searchbar and you'll filter for a item with the given name"
				"- You can &afavorite recipes&r by clicking the &adefault key \"A\"&r"
				"- &ashift + left click&r to craft a bookmarked recipe once"
				"- &actrl + left click&r to craft a bookmarked recipe as much as possible"
			]
			disable_toast: true
