		{
			description: [
				"These quests are not about rewards or progression, they exist to help you understand the modpack. Each quest acts as a tutorial, explaining mechanics, mods, and systems you’ll encounter while playing."
				""
				"There are no item rewards for completing quests. Instead, the real reward is knowledge: learning how things work, avoiding confusion, and surviving longer in this apocalyptic world. "
				""
				"You are free to complete quests at your own pace, in any order, or ignore them entirely. Use this quest book as a reference whenever you’re unsure how something works."
				""
				"Survival is up to you. The quests are here to guide, not to hold your hand."
			]
